        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container px-4 py-5 about-hidden" id="featured-3">
        <h2 class="display-5 fw-bold text-body-emphasis lh-1 mb-3">What We Offer</h2><hr>
        <div class="row g-4 py-5 row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-3">
          <div class="feature col about-hidden">
            <div class="feature-icon d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-2 mb-3">
              <img src="/assets/articles.png" height="100px">
            </div>
            <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">In-Depth Articles</h3>
            <p class="feature-text">Dive into our extensive collection of articles that cover a wide range of topics including technology, lifestyle, travel, health, and more. Our writers are passionate about providing well-researched and engaging content that keeps you informed and entertained.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature col about-hidden">
            <div class="feature-icon d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-2 mb-3">
              <img src="/assets/writing.png" height="100px">
            </div>
            <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Creative Writing</h3>
            <p class="feature-text">Quill Spot is a haven for creative writers. From poetry and short stories to personal essays and fictional tales, our blog showcases the creative talents of writers from all walks of life.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature col about-hidden">
            <div class="feature-icon d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-2 mb-3">
              <img src="/assets/guest.png" height="100px">
            </div>
            <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Guest Contributions</h3>
            <p class="feature-text">We value diverse voices and perspectives. Our platform is open to guest contributors who wish to share their insights and experiences with our readers. If you have a story to tell, Quill Spot is the place for you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container-fluid our-team beige-text about-hidden">
        <div class="row flex-lg-row-reverse align-items-center g-5">
          <div class="col-10 col-sm-8 col-lg-6">
            <img src="/assets/team.png" class="d-block mx-lg-auto img-fluid" alt="Team" width="700" height="500" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold text-body-emphasis lh-1 mb-3">Our Team</h1>
            <p class="lead">Quill Spot is brought to life by a team of dedicated writers, editors, and creatives who are committed to delivering high-quality content. Our team works tirelessly to ensure that every piece published on our blog meets our standards of excellence and resonates with our readers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="px-4 pt-5 my-5 text-center about-hidden">
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-body-emphasis">Join Us On This Journey</h1>
        <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
          <p class="lead mb-4">We invite you to embark on this journey with us. Whether you're here to find inspiration, learn something new, or simply enjoy a good read, Quill Spot is your destination. Together, let's celebrate the magic of words and the stories that shape our world.
            <br><br>
            Thank you for being a part of the Quill Spot community.<br>Happy reading ‚ù§</p>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden" style="max-height: 70vh;">
            <img src="/assets/join.png" class="img-fluid rounded-3 mb-4" alt="Example image" width="400" height="200" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      </div>
      <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            var elements = document.querySelectorAll(".about-hidden");
            var observer = new IntersectionObserver(function(entries) {
                entries.forEach(function(entry) {
                    if (entry.isIntersecting) {
                        entry.target.classList.add("about-fadein");
                        entry.target.classList.remove("about-hidden");
                    }
                });
            });

            elements.forEach(function(element) {
                observer.observe(element);
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>

